        <div class="msgSubject">Glads. Vs. THE STAMINA BARS (was game=268)</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-11-01 00:01:34   | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1288591294260418315" id="quote-1288591294260418315" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1288591294260418315" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=175&amp;mid=1288591294260418315&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1288591294260418315&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_1288591294260418315" onclick="followToggle('add','1288591294260418315')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
